How to apply=20



The first cut-off date for applications is 12-11-2017. (Later applications =
are also welcomed since we anticipate multiple rounds of applications to fi=
ll all 18 positions.) Please send your application via email to application=
s@pads.rwth-aachen.de thereby carefully following the instructions. If you =
have questions, please also use the e-mail address applications@pads.rwth-a=
achen.de .=20



